<h1 align="center">рџљ§ Speed Breaker Detection using Deep Learning</h1>

<p align="center">
A Computer Vision project that detects <b>speed breakers on roads</b> using a Deep Learning model based on <b>MobileNetV2 Transfer Learning</b>.
</p>

<p align="center">

<img src="https://img.shields.io/badge/Python-3.10-blue?logo=python">
