<h2>рџљЂ Installation</h2>

<pre>
git clone https://github.com/Harsh-Mishra0/speed-breaker-detection.git
cd speed-breaker-detection
</pre>

Install required libraries:

<pre>
pip install -r requirements.txt
</pre>

<hr>

<h2>в–¶ Run the Application</h2>

Start the Streamlit application:

<pre>
streamlit run demo/app.py
</pre>

Then open the browser and upload a road image to detect speed breakers.

<hr>

<h2>рџ“Љ Model Training</h2>

<p>
The model was trained using <b>Google Colab</b> with GPU acceleration.
</p>

Training steps:

<ol>
<li>Load dataset</li>
<li>Preprocess road images</li>
<li>Apply transfer learning using MobileNetV2</li>
<li>Train model for multiple epochs</li>
<li>Save trained model (.h5 file)</li>
</ol>

